# Project Structure Guide

This is a **Next.js 15.4.5** application using the **App Router** with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS v4.

## Core Architecture

- **Entry Point**: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with font configuration
- **Main Page**: [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Home page component
- **Global Styles**: [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css) - Tailwind CSS imports and custom styles

## Directory Structure

### `/src/app/` - Next.js App Router
- Contains pages, layouts, and route handlers
- Uses file-based routing system
- Each folder can contain `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `loading.tsx`, `error.tsx`, etc.

### `/src/components/` - Reusable Components
- **`/ui/`** - UI components from shadcn/ui library (e.g., [button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/button.tsx), [dropdown-menu.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/dropdown-menu.tsx))
- Custom application components should go in the root of this directory

### `/src/features/` - Feature-Based Organization
- Currently empty but intended for feature-specific components and logic
- Each feature should be self-contained with its own components, hooks, and utilities

### `/src/lib/` - Shared Utilities
- **[utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts)** - Contains the `cn()` utility for merging Tailwind classes
- Shared functions, constants, and configurations

## Key Configuration Files

- **[package.json](mdc:package.json)** - Dependencies and npm scripts
- **[tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)** - TypeScript configuration with `@/*` path mapping
- **[components.json](mdc:components.json)** - shadcn/ui configuration
- **[next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts)** - Next.js configuration
- **[eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs)** - ESLint configuration
- **[.prettierrc.mjs](mdc:.prettierrc.mjs)** - Prettier formatting rules
